topic: Book Workflow Series ("Author comparison explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining the Italian and French writers who published a book in the last 50 years
goals.2: Compare the number of books written by Italian and French writers
goals.3: Count how many books written by Italian authors are now released with a "public domain" copyright form
goals.4: How many Literature Nobel awards won authors from Italy and from the Kingdom of Italy?
goals.5: Are there books from Litarature Nobel Award winners which are not present in the Vatican Library? (if so, who is the author with more books not in the Vatical Library)?

name: 5965f015f6

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) } LIMIT 50
output: second family name in Spanish name
on focus list of Wikimedia project
organization directed by the office or position

1.query: SELECT ?writer ?writerName (COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBooks) WHERE { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 . ?book <http://schema.org/name> ?bookName . ?writer <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?book wdt:P276 wd:Q213678 } } GROUP BY ?writer ?writerName ORDER BY DESC(?numBooks) LIMIT 1

2.query: SELECT ?numBookIT ?numBookFR WHERE{ { SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBookIT WHERE { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P27 wd:Q38 . } } { SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBookFR WHERE { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P27 wd:Q142 . } } }

SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?writer) AS ?numAwardedWriters) (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?writerName; separator=", ") AS ?winners) WHERE { ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 ; wdt:P27 ?country . ?writer <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName . FILTER (?country = wd:Q38 || ?country = wd:Q172579) }

5.query: SELECT ?country ?countryName AVG(?numBook) AS ?avgBookWritten WHERE{ ?writer wdt:P27 ?country. ?country <http://schema.org/name> ?countryName . { SELECT ?writer COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBook WHERE { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 . } GROUP BY (?writer) } } GROUP BY ?country ?countryName ORDER BY DESC(?avgBookWritten) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?writer ?writerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBook { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 . ?writer <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName . } GROUP BY ?writer ?writerName ORDER BY DESC(?numBook) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?countryName ?numAwardedWriters ?avgBookWritten WHERE{ ?country <http://schema.org/name> ?countryName . { SELECT ?country (COUNT(DISTINCT ?writer) AS ?numAwardedWriters) WHERE { ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 ; wdt:P27 ?country . } GROUP BY ?country } { SELECT ?country AVG(?numBook) AS ?avgBookWritten WHERE{ ?writer wdt:P27 ?country. { SELECT ?writer ?writerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?book) AS ?numBook { ?book (wdt:P31 / wdt:P279*) wd:Q571 ; wdt:P50 ?writer . ?writer wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 ; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 . ?writer <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName . } GROUP BY ?writer ?writerName } } GROUP BY ?country } } ORDER BY DESC(?numAwardedWriters) LIMIT 10
